author: stsp
msg: Prevent a crash which triggered when the move-update editor tried to
merge into a replaced file within the move destination.
(tc_editor_alter_file): If the node to be altered is shadowed by a higher
op-depth layer, don't try to merge new content into the working file.
Instead, we'll have to mark a tree-conflict on this node (which we don't
do yet, but there is a TODO comment telling readers about our plan).
